<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Order Alert - <%= companyName %> Admin</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        .email-container {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 5px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .urgent-banner {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .urgent-banner h3 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .order-alert {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
        }
        .order-alert h2 {
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .order-id {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .order-value {
            background: #22c55e;
            color: white;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .customer-info {
            background: #eff6ff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .customer-info h3 {
            color: #1d4ed8;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .customer-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 12px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .customer-item {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .customer-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .customer-value {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }
        .recipes-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .recipes-table th {
            background: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .recipes-table td {
            padding: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            background: #ffffff;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .total-row {
            background: #f9fafb;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .delivery-info {
            background: #fffbeb;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        }
        .delivery-info h3 {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .action-required {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .action-required h3 {
            color: #166534;
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .action-item {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            text-align: left;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .admin-button {
            background: #22c55e;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 6px 0;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .support-info {
            background: #eff6ff;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .support-info strong {
            color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            .footer {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            .customer-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 10px;
            }
            .recipes-table {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .recipes-table th, .recipes-table td {
                padding: 8px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>New Order Alert</h1>
            <p><%= companyName %> Admin Notification</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="urgent-banner">
                <h3>URGENT: New Order Received</h3>
                <p><strong>Immediate action required!</strong> A customer has placed a new order that needs to be processed.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="order-alert">
                <h2>Order Summary</h2>
                <p class="order-id">Order ID: #<%= orderId.slice(-8).toUpperCase() %></p>
                <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> <%= new Date(createdAt).toLocaleDateString('en-US', {
                    year: 'numeric',
                    month: 'long',
                    day: 'numeric',
                    hour: '2-digit',
                    minute: '2-digit'
                }) %></p>
                <div class="order-value">
                    Total: <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('en-NG', {
                        style: 'currency',
                        currency: 'NGN'
                    }).format(orderAmount) %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="customer-info">
                <h3>Customer Information</h3>
                <div class="customer-details">
                    <div class="customer-item">
                        <div class="customer-label">Customer Name</div>
                        <div class="customer-value"><%= customerName %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="customer-item">
                        <div class="customer-label">Email Address</div>
                        <div class="customer-value"><%= customerEmail %></div>
                    </div>
                    <% if (customerPhone) { %>
                    <div class="customer-item">
                        <div class="customer-label">Phone Number</div>
                        <div class="customer-value"><%= customerPhone %></div>
                    </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                    <div class="customer-item">
                        <div class="customer-label">Phone Number</div>
                        <div class="customer-value" style="color: #6b7280;">Not provided</div>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
                    <div class="customer-item">
                        <div class="customer-label">Order Time</div>
                        <div class="customer-value"><%= new Date(createdAt).toLocaleTimeString('en-US', {
                            hour: '2-digit',
                            minute: '2-digit'
                        }) %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <table class="recipes-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Recipe Ordered</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Price</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% recipes.forEach(recipe => { %>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <strong><%= recipe.name %></strong>
                            <% if (recipe.description) { %>
                            <br><small style="color: #6b7280;"><%= recipe.description %></small>
                            <% } %>
                        </td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">
                            <strong>
                                <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('en-NG', {
                                    style: 'currency',
                                    currency: 'NGN'
                                }).format(recipe.price) %>
                            </strong>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <% }) %>
                    <tr class="total-row">
                        <td><strong>Total Order Value</strong></td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">
                            <strong style="font-size: 18px;">
                                <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('en-NG', {
                                    style: 'currency',
                                    currency: 'NGN'
                                }).format(orderAmount) %>
                            </strong>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="delivery-info">
                <h3>Delivery Information</h3>
                <p><strong>Delivery Address:</strong></p>
                <p style="margin-left: 20px; color: #4a5568; font-size: 15px;">
                    <%= deliveryAddress %><br>
                    <%= deliveryCity %>, <%= deliveryState %>
                </p>
                <p style="background: #ffffff; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 12px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-size: 14px;">
                    <strong>Expected Delivery Window:</strong> 2-4 hours from order confirmation
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="action-required">
                <h3>Immediate Actions Required</h3>

                <div class="action-item">
                    <strong>1. Order Processing:</strong> Review and confirm the order details above
                </div>

                <div class="action-item">
                    <strong>2. Recipe Preparation:</strong> Start preparing the ordered recipes immediately
                </div>

                <div class="action-item">
                    <strong>3. Status Updates:</strong> Update order status as preparation progresses
                </div>

                <div class="action-item">
                    <strong>4. Customer Communication:</strong> Contact customer if any issues arise
                </div>

                <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                    <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>/admin/orders" class="admin-button">Access Admin Panel</a>
                </div>

                <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #166534; margin-top: 12px;">
                    <strong>Customer Contact:</strong> <%= customerEmail %>
                    <% if (customerPhone) { %> | <%= customerPhone %><% } %>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>This notification was sent from the <%= companyName %> order management system.</strong></p>
            <p>Process orders quickly to maintain customer satisfaction!</p>

            <div class="support-info">
                <p><strong>Admin Support:</strong></p>
                <p style="font-size: 13px; margin: 4px 0;">Need technical assistance with order processing?</p>
                <p style="font-size: 13px; margin: 4px 0;">Contact: <strong><%= companyEmail || 'hello@nourishboxng.com.com' %></strong></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">
                    Order Reference: #<%= orderId.slice(-8).toUpperCase() %> | <%= new Date(createdAt).toLocaleDateString() %>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
